{"tid":245911,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"不知不覺分手已經三個月","createTime":"2017-05-16T15:12:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T16:06:33.000Z","uid":60151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c18aeacfaa207112083f157f636784985524e000","tid":245911,"uid":60151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T15:12:05.000Z","msg":"如果你有機會見到個post既話，我想向你問一聲好<br />\n<br />\n分左手三個月我陣唔中都會諗起你，不過我都知我地無機會再係返埋一齊。<br />\n<br />\n當初我咁樣，我承認我都有我做得唔岩既地方。<br />\n<br />\n經過呢三個月冷靜落黎之後，我唔知你過得好唔好，但多謝你 令我對事物有新既睇法。 冷靜落黎之後先發現自己想要既係乜野 <br />\n<br />\n最後我想講既係，同你一齊果段時間我唔辛苦，你無令我後悔。不過走到呢步我已經無力再繼續<br />\n<br />\n心裏面會有你既位置，我係唔會忘記"},{"pid":"19d90d6022b7f49b4984088f079f24c928d2bb07","tid":245911,"uid":116609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T15:14:04.000Z","msg":"想要咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講唔講得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e7660f30375e20be13f35df6e961bb7d0b233fb","tid":245911,"uid":60151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T15:24:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想要咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講唔講得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你指邊方面"},{"pid":"db464d3a16ef2f4e80de33a8c3ec7e15734392df","tid":245911,"uid":116609,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T15:34:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>想要咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講唔講得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你指邊方面</blockquote><br />\n就係唔知先問<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<blockquote>冷靜落黎之後先發現自己想要既係乜野</blockquote>"},{"pid":"8940f8a630767daecd595587253cdfc0cd4d243c","tid":245911,"uid":60151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-16T15:36:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>想